title: Bugged 2016 Season Update page
body:
Just wondering if anyone else has a issue viewing this page and has workaround for it? I'm using Firefox atm but the same issue occurs when I try other browsers. 

This is what I get: http://imgur.com/a/dkR2T

Most of the images display but a lot of others don't including the big picture of Braum, Ori, etc at the top.

replies.body:
Hi,

Thanks for reporting this - there was an issue with the page earlier today, but it should be fixed now.

If you're still seeing it like this, try doing a forced refresh (CTRL+F5)

Cheers
Mindstar
Seems fixed now, thanks for the update.
